<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to SPIN!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome, {{ user.userFname }}!</h1>
        </div>
        <p>Your SPIN account has been created successfully. Here are your login details:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{ user.userEmail }}</li>
            <li><strong>Password:</strong> {{ plainPassword }}</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> For your security, please change your password after logging in.</p>
        <p>
            <a href="{{ loginUrl }}" class="button">Log In Now</a>
        </p>
        <p>If you didnâ€™t create this account, please contact support at amorrions@gmail.com.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The SPIN Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>